net.fortuna.ical4j.model

Class ComponentGroup<T extends Component>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.ComponentGroup<T>

  • public class ComponentGroup<T extends Component>
extends java.lang.Object
    Support for operations applicable to a group of components. Typically this class is used to manage component revisions (whereby each revision is a separate component), and the resulting ouput of such group functins. Created by fortuna on 20/07/2017.
